title: THEY SHALL NOT MOVE ME!!! (Top Lane A-Z: Galio) [League of Legends]

embed.description: Yeah, so I ended up getting Galio Recorded before Fizz, but since I got Fizz recorded during the same day, I decided to stagger Galio to this week! I've began streaming more on Twitch for my recordings, feel free to follow to see things live before they come to Youtube: http://www.twitch.tv/nodragonsplz Feeling tired during gaming sessions?

body: Galio is the very next one! I had a lot of fun with this pick. Galio Smash!
